oru - Abuja The Joint Committees on Appropriations of both the Senate and the House of Representatives have assured that they will submit the harmonised report on the rejigged N13.08 trillion… November 29, 2020 In "News" The House of Representatives has opened the debate on the 2021 Appropriation bill of N13.8 trillion with the view to passing it for second reading. President Muhammadu Buhari had on Thursday, Oct. 8, laid the bill before the house for consideration. Leading the debate, the Majority Leader, Rep. Ado Doguwa… October 14, 2020 In "News"